short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save time and effort with keyboard shortcuts when navigating lists online.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Up and Down saves you time and effort by giving you keyboard shortcuts to quickly navigate any list online. You'll spend less time scrolling and more time getting things done!

Use Up (⇧) and Down (⇩) keys to navigate a common online list. Select it using Enter (⏎). Simple as that.

Works with any of the following:
* Google search results
* Gmail e-mails
* Hacker News posts
* Reddit posts
* Twitter posts

Please send requests to support any new list to support+chrome@sidr.io.
